    metadata: { title: "Crypto Taxes in the UAE & Dubai (2026) | ${SITE_NAME}", description: "Complete guide to cryptocurrency taxes in the UAE and Dubai. Learn about the zero personal income tax policy, corporate tax implications, free zone benefits, and VARA regulatory requirements." },
